        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Indian High Commissioner handed over a statue of Maitri Buddha brought from India to President Ranil Wickremesinghe.",
        "It added that during the discussions they reviewed all-around bilateral cooperation and agreed to further strengthen close India \u2013 Sri Lanka ties in all spheres.",
